      "section_id": "423f7b76-5424-4fbe-bb14-786df6f50545",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "Designed and executed test cases for RL training environments , validating edge cases, evaluation pipelines, and grading logic; identified critical defects in reward functions and collaborated with engineering teams to reduce failure rates across multiple AI evaluation cycles .",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 1,
          "x0": 33.328,
          "y0": 138.47471839999992,
          "x1": 565.4071222400003,
          "y1": 172.67397920000008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "fc8e3dcd-16b4-4ff2-a3ad-e1c438fba200",
      "paper_id": "09190753-7b1e-461b-babe-06c455474b2f",
      "section_id": "423f7b76-5424-4fbe-bb14-786df6f50545",
      "order": 3,
      "text": "Benchmarked frontier model evaluation systems , gaining hands-on exposure to LLM assessment infrastructures.",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 1,
          "x0": 33.627,
          "y0": 174.65871839999988,
          "x1": 535.0702044799998,
          "y1": 186.06397919999995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "f3642bfe-4380-4b62-839f-6413e3348b1d",
      "paper_id": "09190753-7b1e-461b-babe-06c455474b2f",
      "section_id": "c4d10eef-8994-43a4-b1bb-3e97bea29449",
      "order": 0,
      "text": "Architected a full-stack scheduling platform using Next.js, TypeScript, and PostgreSQL with RESTful API design; optimized query execution via indexing and efficient joins, improving API response time by 25% under 50+ concurrent bookings .",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 1,
          "x0": 33.328,
          "y0": 235.64971839999998,
          "x1": 535.2979510399996,
          "y1": 269.8499792000001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "62be8ced-a8c7-4ded-9d71-36b8b6d41b0a",
      "paper_id": "09190753-7b1e-461b-babe-06c455474b2f",
      "section_id": "c4d10eef-8994-43a4-b1bb-3e97bea29449",
      "order": 1,
      "text": "Implemented timezone-aware scheduling logic with automatic client-side detection and conflict resolution, reducing double-booking errors by 30% across distributed users.",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 1,
          "x0": 33.627,
          "y0": 271.89648320000003,
          "x1": 506.2835772799995,
          "y1": 294.63597920000007
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "00664e9c-64d2-486f-bd6c-309b4d33c74f",
      "paper_id": "09190753-7b1e-461b-babe-06c455474b2f",
      "section_id": "c4d10eef-8994-43a4-b1bb-3e97bea29449",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "Deployed on Vercel with environment-based configuration and GitHub-integrated CI workflow; integrated NextAuth for secure authentication and session management.",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 1,
          "x0": 33.627,
          "y0": 296.6207184,
          "x1": 564.5239318399998,
